Seven days and six nights of non-stop pitching.

14:14.540 --> 14:17.510
我个人通常报销5万
I personally clear $50,000 on most trips,

14:17.510 --> 14:21.280
但凭你的功劳
but for everything you've done,

14:21.280 --> 14:22.880
这是你应得的
it's all yours.

14:22.880 --> 14:24.340
我的薄礼
The least I could do.

14:24.340 --> 14:27.010
今天就出发吗
It leaves today?

14:27.010 --> 14:28.380
回家去收拾一下
Go home and pack.

14:28.380 --> 14:30.240
