I'm not going to ask how you're feeling.

15:37.440 --> 15:39.580
很好
Good.

15:39.580 --> 15:42.710
我进"公司"四年后
About four years after I joined the bureau,

15:42.710 --> 15:45.440
我手下第一个特工
my first special agent in charge.

15:45.440 --> 15:47.980
被诊断患有肝癌
he was diagnosed with liver cancer.

15:47.980 --> 15:49.810
