She's got a gun under there.

16:57.410 --> 16:58.650
这就复杂了
It's a complication.

16:58.650 --> 17:00.750
你这么说就对了
Well, that's a nice way to put it.

17:00.750 --> 17:02.650
就像你没拿到第六张卡
Sort of like you not getting the sixth card.

17:02.650 --> 17:04.350
怎么说来着  拖后腿嘛
What are we calling that now, a setback?

17:04.350 --> 17:05.910
放松点
Relax.

17:05.910 --> 17:08.250
你知道我放弃了什么吗
You have any idea what I'm giving up here?

17:08.250 --> 17:09.880
我原本能拿到5万
I was guaranteed 50 grand.

17:09.880 --> 17:12.880
就为5万哭丧着脸  你不是吧
You're crying over $50,000? Are you serious?

17:12.880 --> 17:14.380
我有一份工作
I have a job.

17:14.380 --> 17:16.050
我能赚钱  别人发邮件给我
I make money. I get mail.

17:16.050 --> 17:17.480
都尊呼我  先生
People call me sir.

17:17.480 --> 17:19.780
每天干12小时  吃着残羹剩饭
12-hour days and eating leftover lo-mein.

17:19.780 --> 17:21.480
直觉告诉我  帝博格·巴格维尔
Something tells me Theodore Bagwell

17:21.480 --> 17:23.110
不会坚持太长时间
wouldn't last long in this situation.

17:23.110 --> 17:25.110
可能
Yeah, maybe,

17:25.110 --> 17:27.250
但是科尔·普发会坚持
but Cole Pfeiffer would.

17:27.250 --> 17:29.910
要生气  也要等明天
You want to pout, you do it tomorrow.

17:29.910 --> 17:32.280
我们有事要办
We have work to do.

17:34.810 --> 17:36.810
真的值1.25亿美金吗
Is it really worth $125 million?

17:36.810 --> 17:38.310
价值是两倍
It's worth twice as much.

17:38.310 --> 17:40.410
如果他们不交货呢
What if they refuse to hand it over?

17:40.410 --> 17:43.150
我们要么付钱  要么杀了他们
Either we pay for Scylla, or we kill for it.

17:54.700 --> 17:56.370
苏珊
Susan?

17:56.370 --> 17:59.610
