Hey, give me a second here, guys, just a second.

18:10.150 --> 18:13.150
我们不能发出超过两分贝的噪音
We can't make any noise above ten decibels.

18:13.150 --> 18:15.280
你搞了两个这家伙吗
You got two of those?

18:15.280 --> 18:17.150
是的
Absolutely.

18:18.050 --> 18:19.510
能成功的  对吧
This is gonna work, right?

18:19.510 --> 18:21.180
应该会
It should.

18:21.180 --> 18:23.210
不仅如此
No, not just that.

18:23.210 --> 18:24.850
整个计划
The whole thing.

18:24.850 --> 18:26.950
我们有成功的机会吗
I mean, do we even have a chance?

18:26.950 --> 18:31.010
只要确定打洞的位置准确
Just make sure the hole is in the right place.

18:36.950 --> 18:39.650
进展如何
So, where are we?

18:39.650 --> 18:42.650
格雷琴没有拿到第六张卡
Gretchen didn't get us the sixth card.

18:43.350 --> 18:45.110
我们需要那张卡  唐
We need that sixth card, Don.

18:45.110 --> 18:46.780
我知道
I know.

18:46.780 --> 18:47.560
如果没有那张卡
If we don't get the sixth card,

18:47.560 --> 18:49.280
我们永远无法破解"锡拉"
We're never gonna crack Scylla.

18:49.280 --> 18:50.350
我知道
I know it.

18:50.350 --> 18:53.520
我们还知道什么
What else do we know?

18:54.550 --> 18:56.110
我们知道他们今天就转移"锡拉"
Well, we know they're moving Scylla today.

18:56.110 --> 18:58.350
我们也不能明目张胆地进将军的办公室
We know we can't just waltz into the General's office

18:58.350 --> 18:59.510
偷最后一张卡
and steal that last card,

18:59.510 --> 19:00.750
我们该怎么应对
so where does that leave us?

19:00.750 --> 19:02.180
应该有办法
Then there's got to be a way.

19:02.180 --> 19:03.650
-肯定有办法  -除非再牺牲一个人
There has to be a way. Not without losing another man.

19:03.650 --> 19:05.840
相信我  我用一周时间思考
Believe me, I spent the last week trying to figure out

19:05.840 --> 19:06.920
如何得到第六张卡
how to get that sixth card,

19:06.920 --> 19:08.760
但每种方法的结果都是某人头上顶枪
And every scenario ends with a gun to someone's head,

19:08.760 --> 19:12.050
而这是不可接受的
And that is not acceptable.

19:14.710 --> 19:17.480
格雷琴给了一点
You know, Gretchen did pass on this one piece

19:17.480 --> 19:19.110
信息给你
of information for you.

19:19.110 --> 19:21.480
应该对你有帮助
This could be helpful.

19:28.420 --> 19:30.050
