we need your help.

20:19.150 --> 20:21.750
该走了
It's time to go.

20:25.580 --> 20:28.610
逃跑是最好的办法
"All that avails is flight."

20:28.610 --> 20:31.080
或许我爸爸查到了某些事情
Maybe my father was onto something.

20:31.080 --> 20:33.080
如果因为我们试图搞垮公司
If they all die

20:33.080 --> 20:35.250
他们都死了
because we tried to take down the Company,

20:35.250 --> 20:37.350
