and I survive because...

20:37.350 --> 20:39.810
只是因为我因病离队
because I called in sick...

20:40.680 --> 20:43.080
我自己该如何活下去
...how am I gonna live with myself?

20:52.280 --> 20:54.210
你会好起来的
You're gonna get through this.

20:54.210 --> 20:56.110
