I'm not going to the hospital.

20:56.980 --> 20:58.980
什么
What?

21:00.250 --> 21:02.280
林肯  只管上车吧
Linc, just get in the car.

21:02.280 --> 21:04.650
我和你们一起去
I'm going with you.

21:28.280 --> 21:30.280
如果我还有行医执照的话
If I still had a medical license,

21:30.280 --> 21:32.310
