I'd lose it over this.

21:32.310 --> 21:35.780
这通常是给癫痫病人用的
This is usually given to epileptics.

21:35.780 --> 21:38.110
它能在接下来的3小时内
It will suppress the rapid firing of neurons

21:38.110 --> 21:39.910
抑制神经元快速发放
for the next three hours,

21:39.910 --> 21:41.410
使病情发作的
making it unlikely

21:41.410 --> 21:43.580
可能性变小
that you'll have a seizure in that time,

21:43.580 --> 21:46.480
不过迈克尔  任何精神上或身体上的压力
but Michael, any added mental or physical stress...

21:46.480 --> 21:47.550
