I mean it.

21:48.880 --> 21:51.650
不在万不得已的情况下  我希望你别乱动
I don't want you to move unless you absolutely have to.

21:51.650 --> 21:55.380
等一切结束后  我就带你去医院
And as soon as this is over, I'm taking you to the hospital.

22:08.080 --> 22:10.450
