I promise.

22:16.910 --> 22:20.050
我不是在为自己祈祷
I'm not praying for me.

22:22.850 --> 22:25.510
我们走吧
Let's go.

22:26.180 --> 22:28.250
你要见我
You wanted to see me?

22:28.250 --> 22:30.380
每月的第二个周二
It's the second Tuesday of the month.

22:30.380 --> 22:32.710
