I figured I'd skip it today.

22:36.480 --> 22:39.750
你叫我来就为了确认我的午餐计划吗
You called me in here to confirm my lunch plans?

22:40.510 --> 22:41.850
你是对的
You were right.

22:41.850 --> 22:45.750
如果不是你的提醒  这东西就被偷了
If it weren't for you, this would be in the wind.

22:48.250 --> 22:50.410
-她死了吗  -这样说吧
Is she dead? Let's just say

22:50.410 --> 22:53.080
