Just for, uh, clarification's sake,

23:21.280 --> 23:25.710
第六张卡是待办的一部分  对吧  先生们
the sixth card is part of the to-do list, right, gentlemen?

23:48.750 --> 23:51.110
游戏开始了
The game's afoot.

23:51.110 --> 23:53.650
迈克尔有办法弄到卡吗
Does Michael have a way to get the card?

23:55.510 --> 23:57.110
我和迈克尔·斯科菲尔德交手过
I've worked with Michael Scofield before,

23:57.110 --> 23:58.310
