I don't know. I've set up a safe house

24:15.980 --> 24:18.010
在那可以跟他谈  你有笔吗
where we can hear him out. Do you have a pen?

24:18.010 --> 24:20.310
等一下
Just a minute.

24:23.110 --> 24:24.650
皮尔蒙特街1917号
1917 Piermont.

24:26.810 --> 24:28.250
