Uh, good afternoon.

24:32.880 --> 24:34.710
感谢您致电伽特公司
Thank you for calling Gate.

24:35.580 --> 24:37.150
我要去跟购买商
I got some last minute negotiations

24:37.150 --> 24:38.980
做最后的协商
with the buyer to speak about.

24:38.980 --> 24:40.310
